{"tid":401161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[干預別國內政]中國要求英國勿再發表《香港半年報告書》","createTime":"2017-09-15T11:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T13:23:46.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61e1955eac1015fc3afdb62e072fad8e21a1ea75","tid":401161,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:37:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354269-20170915.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354269-20170915.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=569a147b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354269-20170915.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bf71ab40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354269-20170915.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國政府向國會提交最新一份《香港半年報告書》。在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，香港回歸後的事務屬中國內政，外國無權干預，要求英方不要發表有關報告，停止干預香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩說，香港回歸20年，繼續保持繁榮穩定，「一國兩制」實踐取得了舉世公認的成功。"},{"pid":"67b06d50fdace7c2411459c738229ccc6cc07ed5","tid":401161,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"唔知大陸又會用幾多億叫英國收口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b992932d7c68b84da53f003c53631b7ee9317e0","tid":401161,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781f8d9ed9e2ca45801ce097352b9039cbd259bd","tid":401161,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}